(2, 1, 'custom', 'Homepage', 'rsUni', 'default', '[{\"title\":\"Vermont Bioenergy Initiative Overview\",\"description\":\"Vermont farmers, entrepreneurs and researchers are building an alternative model of bioenergy production that is small-scale, community focused, economical and sustainable.\",\"video\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=6ANoVk4cWwk\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/i1.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/6ANoVk4cWwk\\/hqdefault.jpg\",\"thumb\":\"http:\\/\\/i1.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/6ANoVk4cWwk\\/default.jpg\"},\"animated_blocks\":\"<div class=\\\"rsSBlock Slider h3 SliderH\\\" style=\\\"width: 276px; height: 60px; left: 63%; top: 26%;\\\"><h4>Vermont Bioenergy Initiative<\\/h4><\\/div><div class=\\\"rsSBlock Slider p SliderP\\\" style=\\\"width: 250px; height: 400px; left: 63%; top: 33%;\\\"><p>Vermont farmers, entrepreneurs and researchers are building an alternative model of bioenergy production that is small-scale, community focused, economical, and sustainable.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},{\"title\":\"Algae to Biofuel\",\"description\":\"Vermont researchers and entrepreneurs demonstrate their innovations in algae to biofuel R&D in the Northeast\",\"video\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=7TlEklj7Y1M\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/7TlEklj7Y1M\\/hqdefault.jpg\",\"thumb\":\"http:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/7TlEklj7Y1M\\/default.jpg\"},\"animated_blocks\":\"<div class=\\\"rsSBlock SliderH ui-draggable-handle\\\" style=\\\"width: 250px; height: 60px; left: 63%; top: 26%;\\\"><h4><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/vermontbioenergy.com\\/algae\\/\\\">Algae to Biofuel<\\/a><\\/h4><\\/div><div class=\\\"rsSBlock SliderP ui-draggable-handle\\\" style=\\\"width: 250px; height: 400px; left: 63%; top: 33%;\\\"><p>Vermont researchers and entrepreneurs demonstrate their innovations in algae to biofuel research and development in the Northeast.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},{\"title\":\"Grass Fuel\",\"description\":\"Heating fuels from switchgrass? A Vermont agronomist explains switchgrass production followed by entrepreneurs turning bales of grass into briquette fuel.\",\"video\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=DZ0XYzjis24\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/DZ0XYzjis24\\/hqdefault.jpg\",\"thumb\":\"http:\\/\\/i.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/DZ0XYzjis24\\/default.jpg\"},\"animated_blocks\":\"<div class=\\\"rsSBlock SliderH\\\" style=\\\"width: 250px; height: 60px; left: 63%; top: 26%;\\\"><h4>Grass Fuels<\\/h4><\\/div><div class=\\\"rsSBlock SliderP\\\" style=\\\"width: 250px; height: 400px; left: 63%; top: 33%;\\\"><p>Heating fuels from switchgrass? Sid Bosworth, a University of Vermont agronomist explains switchgrass production followed by biomass entrepreneurs turning bales of grass into briquette fuel.<\\/p><\\/div>\"},{\"title\":\"Making On-Farm Biodiesel\",\"description\":\"Grow oil crops, make biodiesel, feed the animals & save money! Vermont farmer and owner of State Line Biofuels, John Williamson and Chris Callahan, University of Vermont Extension show us how.\",\"video\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/watch?v=sNLdQmXtIO0\",\"image\":\"http:\\/\\/i4.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/sNLdQmXtIO0\\/hqdefault.jpg\",\"thumb\":\"http:\\/\\/i4.ytimg.com\\/vi\\/sNLdQmXtIO0\\/default.jpg\"},\"animated_blocks\":\"<div class=\\\"rsSBlock SliderH\\\" style=\\\"width: 250px; height: 60px; left: 63%; top: 26%;\\\"><h4>Making on-Farm Biodiesel<\\/h4><\\/div><div class=\\\"rsSBlock SliderP\\\" style=\\\"width: 250px; height: 400px; left: 63%; top: 33%;\\\"><p>Grow oil crops, make biodiesel, feed the animals & save money! Vermont farmer and owner of State Line Biofuels John Williamson and University of Vermont Extension\'s Chris Callahan show us how.<\\/p><\\/div>\"}]', '{\"template\":\"default\",\"sopts\":{\"width\":\"100%\",\"height\":\"400px\",\"autoScaleSliderWidth\":\"534\",\"imageScaleMode\":\"fit\",\"imageAlignCenter\":\"false\",\"imageScalePadding\":\"0\",\"arrowsNavAutoHide\":\"false\",\"loop\":\"true\",\"sliderDrag\":\"false\"},\"image_generat