y.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/7-Canola-flower_bee-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Canola Flower & Bee</h3>\n  <p>Canola flower and bee, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11-Canola-seed-pod_August.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11-Canola-seed-pod_August.jpg\" alt=\"Seed Pod\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11-Canola-seed-pod_August-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Seed Pod</h3>\n  <p>Canola seed pod, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/12-Canola-pods_August.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/12-Canola-pods_August.jpg\" alt=\"Canola Pods\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/12-Canola-pods_August-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Canola Pods</h3>\n  <p>Canola pods in August, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/13-Canola_seedpods-at-harvest.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/13-Canola_seedpods-at-harvest.jpg\" alt=\"Seeds at Harvest\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/13-Canola_seedpods-at-harvest-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Seeds at Harvest</h3>\n  <p>Canola pods at harvest, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/14-Borderview-Farm-combine.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/14-Borderview-Farm-combine.jpg\" alt=\"Harvesting Equipment\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/14-Borderview-Farm-combine-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Harvesting Equipment</h3>\n  <p>Combine, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/15-Canola-combined-at-Borderview_VT.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/15-Canola-combined-at-Borderview_VT.jpg\" alt=\"Harvesting Canola\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/15-Canola-combined-at-Borderview_VT-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Harvesting Canola</h3>\n  <p>Harvesting canola with a combine, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/16-Canola-meal-borderview-08.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/16-Canola-meal-borderview-08.jpg\" alt=\"Canola Meal\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/16-Canola-meal-borderview-08-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Canola Meal</h3>\n  <p>Canola meal, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2008. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/17-Canola-oil-etc.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/17-Canola-oil-etc.jpg\" alt=\"Canola\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/17-Canola-oil-etc-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Canola</h3>\n  <p>Canola oil, Borderview Farm, Alburgh Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div></div>\";s:7:\"js_init\";s:670:\"	$(\'.new-royalslider-14\').royalSlider({template:\'default\',image_generation:{imageWidth:\'\',imageHeight:\'\',thumbImageWidth:\'\',thumbImageHeight:\'\'},thumbs:{paddingTop:10,paddingBottom:4,firstMargin:4,thumbWidth:96,thumbHeight:72},fullscreen:{enabled:!0,nativeFS:!0},video:{vimeoCode:\'<iframe src=\\\'http:\\/\\/player.vimeo.com\\/video\\/%id%?byline=0&amp;portrait=0&amp;autoplay=1\\\' frameborder=\\\'no\\\' webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\\/iframe>\'},block:{moveOffset:20,speed:400,delay:200},width:\'100%\',height:500,autoScaleSlider:!0,imageScalePadding:80,controlNavigation:\'thumbnails\',globalCaptionInside:!0,keyboardNavEnabled:!0,fadeinLoadedSlide:!1});\n\";}', 'no'),
