ta-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4Anju_lab-hood.jpg\" alt=\"Researcher in Lab\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/4Anju_lab-hood-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Researcher in Lab</h3>\n  <p>Dr. Anju Dahiya, University of Vermont algae researcher and president of General Systems Research, 2011. <em>Photo credit: General Systems Research</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/5Algepower-racks_Bridport-VT-1024x768.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/5Algepower-racks_Bridport-VT.jpg\" alt=\"Algae Racks\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/5Algepower-racks_Bridport-VT-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Algae Racks</h3>\n  <p>Algepower, Inc. prototype I, Bridport, Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/6Algepower-racks2-Bridport-VT.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/6Algepower-racks2-Bridport-VT.jpg\" alt=\"Algae Racks\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/6Algepower-racks2-Bridport-VT-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Algae Racks</h3>\n  <p>Algepower, Inc. prototype I, Bridport, Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/7CHe-at-ECHO-VT.jpeg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/7CHe-at-ECHO-VT.jpeg\" alt=\"Inoculum Prototype\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/7CHe-at-ECHO-VT-150x150.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Inoculum Prototype</h3>\n  <p>Carbon Harvest Energy‚Äôs first inoculum prototype, University of Vermont Rubenstein School, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/8CHe-Algae-innoculm-closeup.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/8CHe-Algae-innoculm-closeup.jpg\" alt=\"Inoculum Closeup\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/8CHe-Algae-innoculm-closeup-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Inoculum Closeup</h3>\n  <p>Close-up of Carbon Harvest Energy‚Äôs inoculum prototype, Brattleboro, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/9CHe-innoculum-bags-2-1024x768.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/9CHe-innoculum-bags-2.jpg\" alt=\"Algae Researcher\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/9CHe-innoculum-bags-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Algae Researcher</h3>\n  <p>Josh Wilkenfeld, Carbon Harvest Energy, siphons inoculum prior to introducing into the raceway, Brattleboro, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10CHe-J.Wilkenfeld-algae-innoculum-e1437166178469.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10CHe-J.Wilkenfeld-algae-innoculum-e1437166178469.jpg\" alt=\"Algae Researcher\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/10CHe-J.Wilkenfeld-algae-innoculum-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Algae Researcher</h3>\n  <p>Josh Wilkenfeld, Carbon Harvest Energy, siphons inoculum prior to introducing into the raceway, Brattleboro, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11CHe-bottles-and-bags.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11CHe-bottles-and-bags.jpg\" alt=\"Algae Inoculation Lab\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/11CHe-bottles-and-bags-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Algae Inoculation Lab</h3>\n  <p>Carbon Harvest Energy‚Äôs algae inoculation lab, Brattleboro, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/12CHe-J.Wilkenfeld-Inoculating_3.9.12-1024x576.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/12CHe-J.Wilkenfeld-Inoculating_3.9.12.jpg\" alt=\"Raceway Prototype\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/12CHe-J.Wilkenfeld-Inoculating_3.9.12-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Raceway Prototype</h3>\n  <p>Josh Wilkenfeld, Carbon Harvest Energy, introduces algae inoculum into the raceway prototype, Brattleboro, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Carbon Harvest Energy</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/13CHe-Raceway-1024x768.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/13CHe-Raceway.jpg\" alt=\"Raceway\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/13CHe-Raceway-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Raceway</h3>\n  <p>Carbon Harvest Energy‚Äôs algae raceway prototype, Brattleboro, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/16GMS_ReactorwithLamp-1024x764.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/16GMS_ReactorwithLamp.jpg\" alt=\"Prototype Reactor\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/16GMS_ReactorwithLamp-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Prototype Reactor</h3>\n  <p>Green Mountain Spark, LLC, prototype reactor, Burlington, Vermont, 2011. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/17-making-Green-diesel_GMS-1024x768.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/17-making-Green-diesel_GMS.jpg\" alt=\"Green Diesel\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/17-making-Green-diesel_GMS-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Green Diesel</h3>\n  <p>Green Mountain Spark, LLC, making green diesel, Burlington, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18-GMS-sample-Green-Diesel-1024x768.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18-GMS-sample-Green-Diesel.jpg\" alt=\"Green Diesel Sample\"/>\n  <div class=\"rsTmb\"><img src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/18-GMS-sample-Green-Diesel-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n  \n  <h3>Green Diesel Sample</h3>\n  <p>Green Mountain Spark, LLC, sample of green diesel produced in their prototype reactor, Burlington, Vermont, 2012. <em>Photo credit: Vermont Sustainable Jobs Fund</em></p>\n  \n</div><div>\n  <img class=\"rsImg\" src=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/19-M.Faletra_J.Marshall-UVM-algae-1-1024x685.jpg\" data-rsBigImg=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/19-M.Faletra_J.Marshall-UVM-algae-1.jpg\" alt=\"Turbulence Research\"/>\n  <div clas