er</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a title=\"National Advanced Biofuels Conference &amp; Expo.October 26 ‚Äì 28, 2015. Omaha, Nebraska\" href=\"http://www.advancedbiofuelsconference.com/ema/DisplayPage.aspx?pageId=The_Conference___Expo\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\">National Advanced Biofuels Conference &amp; Expo.October 26 ‚Äì 28, 2015.¬†Omaha, Nebraska</span></a></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" title=\"3rd Annual National Bioenergy Day \" href=\"http://vermontbioenergy.com/national-bioenergy-day/#.VSLImfnF91Y\" target=\"_blank\">3<sup>rd</sup> Annual National Bioenergy Day</a></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>November</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;\" title=\"Large-Scale Algal Cultivation, Harvesting and Downstream Processing ‚Äî Novermber 9-13, 2015 ‚Äî Mesa, AZ\" href=\"http://atp3.org/education-and-training/\" target=\"_blank\">Large-Scale Algal Cultivation, Harvesting and Downstream Processing, November 9-13, 2015. Mesa, AZ</a></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Upcoming North American Bioenergy Events', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'upcoming-north-american-bioenergy-events', '', 'http://advancedbiofuelsusa.info/principles-and-processes-algae-culture-maintenance-production-and-downstream-processing-may-18-20-2015-golden-co\nhttp://advancedbiofuelsusa.info/energypath-2015-july-20-24-scranton-pa\nhttp://atp3.org/education-and-training/\nhttp://advancedbiofuelsusa.info/bio-energy-exhibition-conference-2015-fueling-the-new-bioeconomy-may-20-21-toronto-ontario-canada\nhttp://advancedbiofuelsusa.info/microalgal-culture-management-and-strain-selection-august-25-28-2015-austin-tx', '2015-07-17 16:56:39', '2015-07-17 20:56:39', '', 0, 'http://vermo